         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">13/3/81. ¶  ¶ It was my intention, dear Mr Gibbes, to share in the festival of the opening of the Arts Academy yesterday, ¶ The eleventh annual exhibition of the Victorian Academy of Arts.M's invitati...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.03.13</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Francis Gibbes</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 580/1(c), La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation above the date: 'Baron Von Mueller'.</p>
               </note>13/3/81.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was my intention, dear Mr Gibbes, to share in the festival of the opening of the Arts Academy yesterday,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The eleventh annual exhibition of the Victorian Academy of Arts.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's invitation not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but sudden duties arose in connection with the international exhibition in my Department, and I was thus deprived of the pleasure, to attend at the Ceremony. Will you kindly express to the Council of the Academy my best thanks for the honor, done me in inviting me, and also convey my hope, to have at some future occasion the privilege of visiting your noble institution.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
